'''Amirhossein Hosseinzadeh Tazehgheshlagh''' ({{langx|fa|امیرحسین حسین‌زاده}}; born 30 October 2000) is an Iranian [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Winger (football)|winger]] for [[Persian Gulf Pro League]] club [[Tractor S.C.|Tractor]] and the [[Iran national football team|Iran national team]].<ref>{{Soccerway|amirhossein-hosseinzadeh/514128}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=هافبک سایپا اولین خرید استقلال+عکس|work=Vananews agency|url=https://vananews.com/fa/news/425505/%D9%87%D8%A7%D9%81%D8%A8%DA%A9-%D8%B3%D8%A7%DB%8C%D9%BE%D8%A7-%D8%A7%D9%88%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%86-%D8%AE%D8%B1%DB%8C%D8%AF-%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA%D9%82%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%84-%D8%B9%DA%A9%D8%B3}}</ref>

